Ok, works for me.

::Havoc/Repressor::

Havoc flies back toward the Iron Fist, slightly bored. There was no 
battles around, and nothing to do. He taps his comm link, asking 
Zardus for orders. Recieving a reply from FZ several seconds later, 
Havoc turns to the two bots following him.

"Lets go to the Maximal base and check out the situation there. We're 
to aid if needed, but don't be too eager."

He changes course, heading for the Cybertronian Fire.
